3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed method is based on deep learning, and hence, cs.LG is another possible sub-category. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with a task that involves machine learning and NLP, which are both subfields of AI. Hence, cs.AI is another likely sub-category.
